01:22:37,000 --> 01:22:38,000
 Divnu suprugu imate.

1365
01:22:38,000 --> 01:22:40,000
 Ponekad malo više se snima na ljutršani.

1366
01:22:40,000 --> 01:22:41,000
 Jeste čuli što sam rekla?

1367
01:22:41,000 --> 01:22:42,000
 Pona hvala.

1368
01:22:42,000 --> 01:22:44,000
 Divnu suprugu imate.

1369
01:22:44,000 --> 01:22:46,000
 Nemojte slučajno to preskakati, ali i psa.

1370
01:22:46,000 --> 01:22:49,000
 Jako sam ovaj, moja supruga super.

